  - m_Id: 5866143773
    m_Localized: Raw Wood
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143774
    m_Localized: Advanced electronic components including circuits, wiring, and control
      systems. Essential for modern machinery, vehicles, and sophisticated devices.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143775
    m_Localized: A prime mover engine converting fuel energy into mechanical power.
      Powers machinery, vehicles, and industrial equipment through combustion or steam.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143776
    m_Localized: Woven textile material made from natural or synthetic fibers. Essential
      for clothing, upholstery, and various household items.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143777
    m_Localized: High-quality wood with a smooth finish and beautiful grain. Selected
      and perfected through meticulous processing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143778
    m_Localized: Essential mechanical components including bolts, gears, and structural
      elements. The foundation of all machinery, construction, and industrial production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143779
    m_Localized: Professional-grade steel tools including power drills and precision
      wrenches. Essential for factory maintenance and machinery production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143780
    m_Localized: Exceptional timber of unmatched quality and elegance. Reserved for
      masterwork creations and items of great value.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143781
    m_Localized: Simple, durable clothing made from basic fabric. Practical and comfortable
      for everyday wear.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143782
    m_Localized: Simple, functional furniture crafted from fine wood. Practical and
      affordable, suitable for everyday use.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143783
    m_Localized: A basic household tool set including hammer, saw, and wrench. Essential
      for everyday repairs and furniture assembly. A consumer staple.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143784
    m_Localized: High-quality clothing crafted from fine materials with exquisite tailoring.
      A mark of elegance and sophistication.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143785
    m_Localized: Exquisite furniture crafted from premium wood with fine details and
      elegant design. A symbol of luxury and refined taste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143786
    m_Localized: Lightweight aluminum bar with exceptional strength. Used in aircraft,
      vehicles, and modern structures.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143787
    m_Localized: Refined copper bar with excellent electrical conductivity. The backbone
      of modern electrical systems.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143788
    m_Localized: A solid bar of smelted iron, forged from raw ore. Versatile and durable,
      ready for crafting.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143789
    m_Localized: Refined gold of the highest purity, gleaming with warm radiance. A
      symbol of wealth and craftsmanship excellence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143790
    m_Localized: High-quality steel forged from refined iron through advanced smelting.
      Stronger and more durable than pure iron.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143791
    m_Localized: Lightweight and strong metal. Material for aircraft and advanced vehicles.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143792
    m_Localized: Essential fuel for smelting iron into steel.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143793
    m_Localized: Highly conductive metal. Essential for electronic component production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143794
    m_Localized: Rare precious metal. Core material for luxury goods.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143795
    m_Localized: The foundation of industry. The primary material for steel and machine
      parts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143796
    m_Localized: Black gold. Material for synthetic textiles, plastics, and fuel for
      tanks and aircraft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143797
    m_Localized: The most basic resource. Material for furniture, tools, and early
      textiles (pulp).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143798
    m_Localized: The ruler of the skies. Requires aluminum and advanced electronic
      equipment. The pinnacle of precision industry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143799
    m_Localized: The product of modern engineering. A luxury item for the wealthy during
      peaceful times. Demand plummets during war as civilians become impoverished.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143800
    m_Localized: The king of ground warfare. A combination of steel and heavy artillery.
      Consumes massive amounts of steel and heavy arms during wartime production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143801
    m_Localized: High-value strategic weapons. Field artillery and anti-aircraft guns
      that can change the course of battle. Extremely high profit margin for prepared
      manufacturers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143802
    m_Localized: The fuel of war. Bullets, shells, and explosives consumed continuously
      as long as conflict persists. Demand becomes nearly infinite during wartime.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5866143803
    m_Localized: Basic infantry weapons including rifles, pistols, and combat knives.
      Essential equipment for conscripted soldiers. Demand explodes at the start of
      war.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
